# Revisions  :
# Date        Version  Author   Description
# 2025-03-22  1.0.0    mrosiere Created
# 2025-04-05  1.1.0    mrosiere Add Algo
# 2025-05-08  1.2.0    mrosiere Change to into downto
# 2025-09-05  1.2.1    mrosiere Add Package
# 2025-11-22  1.2.2    mrosiere Use sbi instead pbi
# 2026-01-18  1.2.3    mrosiere Use info record of sbi
# 2026-05-22  1.3.0    mrosiere Add explicit default slave
# 2026-06-02  1.3.1    mrosiere Fix multi driver
# 2026-06-05  1.3.2    mrosiere Add default slave dedicated port option
